#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a po file from two DocBook XML files"
msgstr "DocBook XML सञ्चिकाद्वयात् po सञ्चिकां निर्माति"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>split2po</command> <group choice=\"req"
"\"><option><replaceable>Original-XML</replaceable></option> "
"<option><replaceable>Translated-XML</replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>विभक्त२पो</command><group choice=\"req\"><option><replaceable> मूल-"
"XML</replaceable></option><option><replaceable> अनुवादित-XML</replaceable></"
"option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>split2po</command> is a command-line tool that takes the two given "
"DocBook XML files and produces a <command>gettext</command> message file (PO-"
"file) that represents the changes between them. The resulting PO-file is "
"sent to standard output."
msgstr ""
"<command>split2po</command> इति आदेशपङ्क्तिसाधनं यत् दत्तद्वयं DocBook XML सञ्चिकां "
"गृहीत्वा <command>gettext</command> सन्देशसञ्चिकां (PO-file) उत्पादयति यत् तयोः मध्ये "
"परिवर्तनं प्रतिनिधियति परिणामी PO-सञ्चिका मानकनिर्गमं प्रति प्रेष्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<filename>translated-XML</filename> must be the result of translating "
"<filename>original-XML</filename> into another language. It is this "
"translation that the resulting PO-file will represent."
msgstr ""
"<filename>translated-XML</filename> इत्येतत् <filename>original-XML</filename> "
"इत्यस्य अन्यभाषायां अनुवादस्य परिणामः भवितुमर्हति । अयं अनुवादः एव परिणामी PO-सञ्चिका "
"प्रतिनिधित्वं करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-split2po.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr "इयं उपयोगिता KDE Software Development Kit इत्यस्य भागः अस्ति ।"

